    tmp = 0.86

    tmp = wp.exp(v1)
    tmp = (v0 + wp.exp((v2 + 0.88 * tmp + 0.63)))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.66) - (v1 + 0.73 + v1 + 0.66)) + wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.56)))
